Newport Electronics Inc. of Santa Ana, Calif., na im dey hold di 49.4% stake, e come ask special shareholder meeting next Wednesday to remove four current directors, e elect alternative slate.

For August, Mr. Hollander's High Technology Holding Co, of Stamford, Conn. E get most of im stake last August for one $11-a share tender offer wey dem dey give Newport wey be electronic measuring device.

Newport talk sey Oga Hollander dey ask shareholders to retain only one director, James R. Lees, a Newport vice president.

Di board no dey propose slate of its own, and di four current directors no wan do beyond di special session date, Newport talk.

Oga Hollander sey na di new owner na im wan do exercise, na im e con talk sey Barret B. Weekes, Newport chairman o.

